snippet.title: Best VGM 1413 - Gran Turismo 5 - Sunset Haze
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2068 - https://youtu.be/MbkMki62A4o

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS3
Gran Turismo 5 (2010)
Sunset Haze
Keiji Inai
